Apple today shared a new <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3-Y6QLFHTlA">"Slide" ad</a> that highlights the Ceramic Shield 2 cover glass on the iPhone 17, iPhone 17 Pro, and iPhone 17 Pro Max.<br/>
<br/>
